&lt;p&gt;Serve as a strategic finance partner to Product, Growth Analytics, Credit, Revenue, and Merchant Pricing, influencing product strategy, investment decisions, and go-to-market execution&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
