&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Develop deep expertise in transactional unit economics and customer lifetime value (LTV), and use these frameworks to guide prioritization and resource allocation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lead top-line planning processes, including target setting, forecasting, and performance tracking; deliver clear, concise reporting and insights to executives and senior leadership&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Build and scale automated dashboards, reporting, and analytical frameworks to improve visibility and decision-making across the organization&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Identify key drivers of performance, surface risks and opportunities, and drive accountability against business goals&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Synthesize complex analyses into clear, compelling narratives that inform strategic decisions and align cross-functional stakeholders&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
