&lt;p&gt;Proven ability to operate with ownership and influence in a fast-paced, ambiguous environment, with strong critical thinking and problem-solving skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;10+ years of experience in analytical roles (e.g., strategic finance, investment banking, consulting, data science, or analytics), with demonstrated impact on business outcomes and forecasting&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
