&lt;p&gt;Strong business judgment, with the ability to connect detailed analyses to broader strategic context and executive-level decisions&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience partnering with senior stakeholders and influencing decisions across cross-functional teams&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Expert in financial modeling; working knowledge of SQL and experience with data visualization tools (e.g., Sigma or similar) preferred&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
